We collect personal information from you, including information about your:

•	Name
•	Contact information
•	Computer or network

We collect your personal information in order to:

•	Connect people for social networking

Besides our staff, we share this information with:

•	Youtube in order to suggest users their favorite videos.
•	Whatsapp in order to see if users already using whatsapp service

Providing some information is optional. If you choose not to enter Name and date of birth, we'll not be able to let them create their profile.
We keep your information safe by storing in encrypted files and only allowing few staff access to it.
We keep your information for 2 years at which point we securely destroy it by securely deleting it.
You have the right to ask for a copy of any personal information we hold about you, and to ask for it to be corrected if you think it is wrong. If you’d like to ask for a copy of your information, or to have it corrected, please contact us at sfar211@mywhitecliffe.com.
